{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/idp/","result":{"data":{"post":{"id":"e6912584-fd19-5d68-8c8a-ee9001dcff46","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/bc3ae/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"logo\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/5a190/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/772e8/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png 200w,\n/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/e17e5/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png 400w,\n/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/5a190/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png 800w,\n/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/c1b63/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png 1200w,\n/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/bc3ae/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png 1268w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<h2>International Drivers Permit</h2>\n<h3>Because why not?</h3>\n<p>And I really mean it. It only took 10 minutes at <a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Club+Travel/@-33.8739,18.6325253,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x1dcc50b0a9f27947:0x7b9456a4dd638a4c!8m2!3d-33.8739!4d18.634714\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Club Travel</a> in Tygervalley mall which is 5 minutes drive from our house. </p>\n<p>Technically for South Africans to be allowed to drive legally in the UK, you only need your South African drivers license, however the small print for any insurrance be it a hired vehicle or anyone elses vehicle state, that if you do not have an IDP that was issued before the accident, they will not pay out any cover.</p>\n<p>So I went out to get one, just in case I do need it.</p>\n<p>Front:\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cb6369a6b3a730cedbd7fe84a1ffbee6/6e52e/IMG-20190729-WA0005.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 648px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 177.99999999999997%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"idp-front\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/cb6369a6b3a730cedbd7fe84a1ffbee6/6e52e/IMG-20190729-WA0005.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cb6369a6b3a730cedbd7fe84a1ffbee6/e07e9/IMG-20190729-WA0005.jpg 200w,\n/static/cb6369a6b3a730cedbd7fe84a1ffbee6/066f9/IMG-20190729-WA0005.jpg 400w,\n/static/cb6369a6b3a730cedbd7fe84a1ffbee6/6e52e/IMG-20190729-WA0005.jpg 648w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Inside:\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/522b1564e6cc76a581a1c662b814b9ae/5ef17/IMG-20190729-WA0006-public.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"idp-inside\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/522b1564e6cc76a581a1c662b814b9ae/4b190/IMG-20190729-WA0006-public.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/522b1564e6cc76a581a1c662b814b9ae/e07e9/IMG-20190729-WA0006-public.jpg 200w,\n/static/522b1564e6cc76a581a1c662b814b9ae/066f9/IMG-20190729-WA0006-public.jpg 400w,\n/static/522b1564e6cc76a581a1c662b814b9ae/4b190/IMG-20190729-WA0006-public.jpg 800w,\n/static/522b1564e6cc76a581a1c662b814b9ae/5ef17/IMG-20190729-WA0006-public.jpg 1152w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>","fields":{"slug":"/idp/","prefix":"2019-07-29"},"frontmatter":{"title":"International Drivers Permit","author":"david bezuidenhout","category":"news","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/5fd3384f98bb53a84332743d0dbd8c49/630fb/undraw_open_source_1qxwr.png"}}}}},"authornote":{"id":"3abb2b0f-e07d-5a66-bc29-fd668c961a0c","html":"<p><strong>David Bezuidenhout</strong> I’m a sysadmin, network-admin and a cloud support engineer. I’m open to any suggestions from anyone. Feel free to let me know what you think.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/idp/","prev":{"id":"1eee3734-d757-5df3-94b1-02da319d37e2","fields":{"slug":"/suitcases/","prefix":"2019